# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Python Monorepo - .dockerignore
# Used for root-level Docker builds; each app has its own Dockerfile
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Ignore everything.
**

# Except the following common monorepo files.
!pyproject.toml
!uv.lock
!README.md
!LICENSE.txt
!libs/
!.env.example

# Filter unwanted files from included folders.
**/__pycache__
**/*.py[cod]
**/*.pyo
**/*.pyd
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/.DS_Store
**/.venv
**/.pytest_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/.mypy_cache
**/*.egg-info/
**/.coverage
**/htmlcov/
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/build/
**/.nox/